snippet.title: Legend of Merchant - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
A small, indie game that is about trading goods, as you need to make wise decisions in order to make as much money as possible within 100 days.

Legend of Merchant (C) CrazyPrince
Steam link: https://store.steampowered.com/app/543140/Legend_of_Merchant/
